                        <interp inst="t18421024-2938-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 32.—
<rs id="t18421024-2938-punishment-149" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18421024-2938-punishment-149" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2938-18421024 t18421024-2938-punishment-149"></join>Transported for Fifteen Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
